title: Per Capita Personal Consumption Expenditures: Services: Final Consumption Expenditures of Nonprofit Institutions Serving Households for Far West BEA Region
notes:
Personal consumption expenditures of a given area divided by the resident population of the area.

Net expenses of NPISHs, defined as their gross operating expenses less primary sales to households.For more information about this release go to http://www.bea.gov/newsreleases/regional/pce/pce_newsrelease.htm.
